{"type":"answer","id":53452,"parentType":"question","parentId":12245,"uid":6760,"contents":"他造的假新闻都火到品葱辣，大家还都把这当真新闻讨论呐。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/23520\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【人为粮荒】其实所有人都忽略了，粮食危机也许并不因为粮食短缺本身。</a>（<a href=\"https://archive.is/WleYp\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">快照</a>）<br>\n赶紧叫他在标题标注上【假新闻乳共】吧，趁着两站加速党还没翻大车前。<br>\n<hr><br>\n去年11月份，类似的事情就在品葱上演过。用户“高雅人”发布了类似的p出来的共青团知乎回答，并声称是真新闻，且成功使得成百上千人上当受骗。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/10366\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">如何看待共青团中央力挺《少年的你》抄袭东野圭吾？</a>（<a href=\"https://archive.is/9v2W9\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">快照</a>）<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/7388\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">删帖控平</a>（<a href=\"https://archive.is/tIpkB\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">快照</a>）<br>\n<br>\n明知道是假消息，TA却这么说：<br>\n<blockquote>管理员置顶一下可以吗，这个很重要，要让日本看到</blockquote><br>\n（<a href=\"https://archive.is/tIpkB#selection-1095.0-1109.4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">快照</a>）<br>\n<br>\n在共青团发表了辟谣帖后，TA仍然“精神胜利”<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/7432\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">昨晚共青团中央的截图事件做得非常成功，我们大胜</a>（<a href=\"https://archive.is/8yr2n\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">快照</a>）<br>\n后来因为伪造假新闻被封禁了，可喜可贺。<br>\n<br>\n然后后来又有个“<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E5%BB%A2%E9%9D%92%E5%9C%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">廢青團中央</a>”，用同样的手段发布假新闻。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/23851\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">如何看待看待共青团中央“95%美国人不配活着”的野蛮暴论？</a><br>\n<br>\n不久后也被封了。","date":"2020-09-06","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}